{
 "name": "RPlog_Mission_to_Ord_Mantell",
 "title": "Mission to Ord Mantell",
 "summary": "Dispatched aboard the Tortuga to reunite a family, the Horansi agent Kasha and her companion Tiali track down Casul Nettic on Ord Mantell, the father of two younglings recovered safely to Caspar. Wary after being repeatedly swindled by a sham detective tied to the Nova Syndicate, the impoverished Casul slowly comes to believe the charitable offer and points the agents toward his estranged wife Sasha, a waitress at the Cat's Claw Cantina. After coaxing the bickering couple to reconcile and accept passage off-world, the agents shepherd them toward the docking bay, only for the Nova debt-collector Coxswain and his armed goons to ambush them. A brawl and firefight erupt as Kasha's own father, coerced into working for Nova, unexpectedly appears, and the agents fight to bundle the family safely aboard the ship.",
